WEBVTT

00:16.559 --> 00:18.728
<i>♪ Young man goes out ♪</i>

00:18.811 --> 00:24.275
<i>♪ Looking for the diamond in the sea ♪</i>

00:27.362 --> 00:31.699
<i>♪ Old man rows his boat to shore ♪</i>

00:31.783 --> 00:35.370
<i>♪ And falls on twisted knees ♪</i>

00:37.830 --> 00:44.462
<i>♪ And you'll drown</i>
<i>Before the water lets you in ♪</i>

00:47.090 --> 00:53.054
<i>♪ And you'll drown</i>
<i>Before the water lets you in ♪♪</i>

01:40.768 --> 01:42.937
I gotta know, John.

01:54.407 --> 01:55.950
About what?

01:59.662 --> 02:01.706
They said he drowned.

02:05.627 --> 02:07.462
So, you did--

02:08.755 --> 02:10.089
What?

02:16.179 --> 02:18.264
How did it happen?

02:43.456 --> 02:45.667
You wanted me to let you know

02:45.750 --> 02:48.294
if ever there was a time we were not safe.

02:51.422 --> 02:53.174
Yeah.

02:56.969 --> 02:59.013
Things are not good.

03:04.435 --> 03:07.563
What the fuck
am I supposed to do with that?

03:08.439 --> 03:10.817
There's information about me
out there that...

03:11.025 --> 03:12.318
What kind of information?

03:12.527 --> 03:13.444
...could be bad for me.

03:13.528 --> 03:14.570
What--?

03:18.282 --> 03:19.409
Can...?

03:20.076 --> 03:21.452
Can you do--?

03:21.536 --> 03:25.164
Can you get rid of it? Isn't there
something you can do to make it go away?

03:25.331 --> 03:27.125
It's not like that.

03:35.591 --> 03:39.011
Do whatever it is that you have to do.

03:50.481 --> 03:52.191
Don't come home tonight.

03:55.528 --> 03:58.072
I'll tell the kids something.
I don't know, but I...

03:58.823 --> 04:01.159
I can't fucking look at you right now.

04:35.359 --> 04:36.903
Where'd you find this?

04:37.612 --> 04:38.988
On the beach.

04:39.197 --> 04:42.617
Where John met with Danny
the morning after the Red Reef.

04:42.825 --> 04:44.660
Did you see John that morning?

04:45.161 --> 04:46.370
Nope.

04:46.454 --> 04:50.166
No, I took off before John got there,
but then I went back later on,

04:50.249 --> 04:53.127
and I found that there.
Danny gave that to Janey.

04:53.377 --> 04:54.962
And John took it from her.

04:55.171 --> 04:57.006
John had to be at the beach.

04:57.423 --> 04:59.467
So, why is he lying, saying he wasn't?

04:59.550 --> 05:00.927
It's fucking two plus two.

05:01.302 --> 05:03.429
John wanted Lowry's guy to take Danny out.

05:03.513 --> 05:04.722
It didn't work.

05:04.806 --> 05:08.392
So, then John's gotta go
take care of his own fucking business.

05:10.144 --> 05:12.230
I'm gonna get you your immunity.

06:10.371 --> 06:11.831
Eric was there?

06:14.458 --> 06:15.668
What did he see?

06:20.006 --> 06:22.341
I don't know if he saw anything,
but he must know something

06:22.425 --> 06:25.386
or else Marco wouldn't be trying
to get him immunity.

06:30.891 --> 06:34.395
Marco would have to have a warrant
to access the cameras.

06:34.604 --> 06:37.231
But as long as Internal Affairs
is investigating him,

06:37.315 --> 06:39.442
he can't do a goddamn thing.

06:41.861 --> 06:43.237
You leaked it?

06:45.114 --> 06:46.407
I did.

07:02.131 --> 07:05.593
If Internal Affairs clears Marco,
then he's free to go after this.

07:05.801 --> 07:07.637
The investigation could take weeks.

07:07.720 --> 07:10.014
Depending on what they find,
it could take months.

07:10.139 --> 07:12.475
That doesn't get rid of the problem, John.

07:13.851 --> 07:15.853
Eric O'Bannon doesn't go away.

07:16.812 --> 07:19.148
Whatever he knows, he still knows.

07:21.692 --> 07:23.819
Meg, you know whatever happens...

07:24.987 --> 07:27.365
I will take responsibility
for all of this.

07:27.573 --> 07:30.743
John, we're on those tapes with you.

07:31.369 --> 07:35.206
There is-- There's no scenario where
you confess and we come out clean.

07:38.709 --> 07:41.128
Jesus. I gotta call Kevin.

07:41.337 --> 07:42.421
Don't do that.

07:46.258 --> 07:49.637
I'm not gonna keep hiding shit, John.

07:50.179 --> 07:54.517
All I do is I fucking lie.
I lie and I lie. I'm fucking sick of it.

07:55.601 --> 07:56.686
I can't do this.

07:57.144 --> 07:59.772
I can't, I can't, I can't.
You know what? I'm sorry. I just...

07:59.855 --> 08:01.315
I just-- I have to go.

08:04.276 --> 08:06.487
This is all about Eric O'Bannon now.

08:06.570 --> 08:10.449
If he doesn't talk,
then Marco doesn't have anything.

08:23.129 --> 08:25.131
She's right, you know, John.

08:29.510 --> 08:31.262
All about Eric.

08:35.433 --> 08:37.184
My good friend Eric.

08:41.731 --> 08:43.691
Of all the people in the world...

08:46.861 --> 08:48.696
He's really got you, though.

08:53.075 --> 08:54.577
What are you gonna do about it?

09:02.501 --> 09:04.879
Oh, those are dark thoughts.

09:08.424 --> 09:09.675
Dark.

09:10.718 --> 09:12.053
Dark thoughts.

09:21.103 --> 09:22.396
Be careful on the water.

09:22.480 --> 09:23.481
-Okay.
-Thanks.

09:23.564 --> 09:24.607
Bye-bye.

09:32.490 --> 09:33.991
Hello.

09:34.492 --> 09:35.868
Oh, wow.

09:36.702 --> 09:39.997
Wow. You... You look just like him.

09:40.414 --> 09:41.624
I'm sorry?

09:42.249 --> 09:44.293
Danny. Danny. I mean...

09:44.376 --> 09:45.920
I mean, the resemblance.

09:47.630 --> 09:49.840
Oh, um...

09:51.133 --> 09:52.760
Can I help you with something?

09:53.219 --> 09:55.304
I was a good friend of his.

09:55.721 --> 09:56.764
My son?

09:57.264 --> 09:58.390
We were very close.

09:58.474 --> 10:00.559
We used to hang out in Miami all the time.

10:01.644 --> 10:03.020
And how do you know him?

10:03.562 --> 10:06.899
Oh, through a mutual friend.
Eve Radosevich?

10:07.108 --> 10:08.192
Oh, yeah.

10:08.275 --> 10:10.820
She's the reason I'm here.
I just came to visit.

10:12.571 --> 10:16.033
God, this place... This place is sick.

10:16.117 --> 10:17.535
Oh, my God.

10:18.327 --> 10:19.453
Look at this.

10:20.663 --> 10:23.165
I don't know what the hell
Danny was talking about.

10:23.249 --> 10:24.583
Always complaining.

10:24.792 --> 10:27.419
If I'd have grown up here,
I'd have never left.

10:28.295 --> 10:29.797
I'd like to stay here.

10:29.880 --> 10:32.049
Hey, hey, you need a bellhop?
Because I'm available.

10:32.133 --> 10:33.509
Just putting it out there.

10:34.051 --> 10:36.053
Uh, does Eve know you're here?

10:36.846 --> 10:38.347
You know, I was...

10:38.430 --> 10:41.016
I was a bellhop all through high school.

10:41.809 --> 10:44.395
We didn't own the hotel like you people.
My mom was a...

10:44.854 --> 10:47.690
She was just a maid.
That's how she got me the job.

10:47.898 --> 10:50.484
Because one of those
big families, seven kids.

10:50.568 --> 10:53.612
You don't work, you don't eat.
Bottom line, you know?

10:55.906 --> 10:57.116
Hey.

10:57.491 --> 11:00.536
You know,
I remember once Danny told me that you--

11:00.619 --> 11:01.912
You had a...

11:02.329 --> 11:04.081
A little girl that drowned?

11:06.625 --> 11:07.835
Yes.

11:08.919 --> 11:10.963
Danny was really broken up about that.

11:11.881 --> 11:14.508
And I know how he felt because

11:14.717 --> 11:16.468
I had a little kid brother who...

11:17.011 --> 11:18.012
who died.

11:18.971 --> 11:19.972
Shot.

11:20.139 --> 11:21.307
A stray bullet.

11:23.475 --> 11:24.685
I'm very sorry.

11:27.271 --> 11:28.355
But you know what?

11:29.064 --> 11:30.107
We never...

11:30.524 --> 11:34.028
We never felt sorry for ourselves,
you know, the way that Danny did.

11:34.820 --> 11:37.531
We just went in the world,
and did what you had to do.

11:38.991 --> 11:41.535
I don't know,
I guess you got a name like Rayburn,

11:41.744 --> 11:44.163
I mean, and a place like this...

11:45.497 --> 11:47.207
That's a lot to live up to.

11:47.416 --> 11:50.085
I mean, you gotta hide all the rough edges

11:50.294 --> 11:52.671
and keep up appearances,
and it must make you...

11:52.880 --> 11:54.381
Must make you have to do some...

11:55.257 --> 11:56.800
really funny things.

12:00.054 --> 12:01.055
You know what I mean?

12:02.640 --> 12:04.516
No, I don't.

12:07.645 --> 12:09.647
Oh. Oh, there she is.

12:09.855 --> 12:10.773
Eve.

12:11.607 --> 12:13.150
Your friend is here.

12:18.697 --> 12:20.157
Uh...

12:20.240 --> 12:21.367
Hey.

12:23.911 --> 12:25.704
You should've told me you were coming.

12:26.580 --> 12:27.706
Surprise.

12:31.919 --> 12:33.837
But now's not a good time, you know?

12:35.547 --> 12:37.049
Oh, really?

12:37.132 --> 12:39.551
-But we'll talk later, all right?
-Okay.

12:40.803 --> 12:42.137
We'll talk later.

12:44.056 --> 12:46.475
Hey, so it was so good to meet you.
What a pleasure.

12:46.558 --> 12:50.270
Looking forward to seeing more of you,
now that Eve's part of the family.

12:51.438 --> 12:54.984
Hey, hey, don't be a stranger. Come on.
You and I got a lot to catch up on.

13:05.911 --> 13:08.872
So, O'Bannon's telling you
that John met with Danny?

13:08.956 --> 13:11.959
According to him, John and Danny
were to meet the next morning.

13:12.042 --> 13:15.629
So, the theory that John helped Danny
after the Red Reef, it fits.

13:18.757 --> 13:19.925
Yeah.

13:22.094 --> 13:25.014
It is still your theory, right?
Or are you thinking of something else?

13:25.472 --> 13:26.390
Look, I...

13:28.142 --> 13:30.978
I just wanna get immunity for O'Bannon
and see where it goes.

13:31.061 --> 13:32.104
Yeah, well...

13:32.730 --> 13:34.481
you're gonna have to wait on that.

13:35.232 --> 13:38.193
I just got a call from
the commissioner's office this morning.

13:38.652 --> 13:43.490
Until the investigation is over, the DA's
office will not accept requests from us.

13:44.158 --> 13:45.242
Fuck.

13:45.534 --> 13:46.452
If we could...

13:47.619 --> 13:49.997
get out from under IA,
they said they'd play ball.

13:51.123 --> 13:52.875
And if we don't? Hmm?

13:55.794 --> 13:58.672
-When do you talk to IA again?
-Uh, tomorrow morning.

13:59.631 --> 14:00.799
Right.

14:00.883 --> 14:02.885
Forget about O'Bannon right now.

14:03.927 --> 14:05.971
That's what we gotta worry about.

14:12.269 --> 14:13.562
Jake the Snake!

14:13.771 --> 14:16.065
-Kev, what's up, baby?
-Hey, man.

14:17.357 --> 14:19.943
- How you doing, man?
- I'm all right.

14:22.738 --> 14:23.864
How you been?

14:24.031 --> 14:25.407
I'm good, man.

14:28.410 --> 14:30.704
God, it's good to see you.
Thanks for coming down.

14:31.121 --> 14:34.124
So, listen, I just wanted to say, um...

14:34.208 --> 14:37.127
well, the last time I saw you,
I was...

14:37.878 --> 14:39.088
I was not...

14:39.171 --> 14:41.632
- I was in a very bad place.
- You think? You...?

14:41.715 --> 14:43.509
Yeah.

14:43.592 --> 14:44.635
And, um...

14:45.427 --> 14:48.389
You know, but I heard what you said.
I had too much on my plate.

14:48.555 --> 14:49.640
And, um...

14:50.933 --> 14:53.352
But things are going well for me now.
I stopped drinking.

14:53.560 --> 14:55.437
-Yeah, yeah, I heard. I heard.
-Did you?

14:55.521 --> 14:56.814
Yeah, that's good, man. I'm...

14:57.314 --> 14:59.817
- I'm proud of you, man.
- Yeah, I...

15:00.150 --> 15:01.151
I'm feeling good.

15:01.860 --> 15:03.153
Good. You look good.

15:04.405 --> 15:06.115
So, you interested
in your old job back?

15:06.323 --> 15:08.617
-My old job here?
-Yeah, your old job here, asshole.

15:08.700 --> 15:10.536
-I don't know, I don't know.
-Come on.

15:11.286 --> 15:13.831
Let me think about it.

15:13.914 --> 15:16.375
I'll be interested in my old salary,
how about that?

15:16.583 --> 15:18.168
Yeah? How about a ten percent bump?

15:19.169 --> 15:21.713
My man. Thank you, man.
It's good to see you, man.

15:21.797 --> 15:23.424
- Good to see you, too.
- Hey.

15:23.507 --> 15:25.300
-Hey.
-Who's the new guy?

15:25.509 --> 15:27.344
Jake's not new.
He's one of my oldest friends.

15:27.428 --> 15:29.763
He's worked for me forever.
The best mechanic in the Keys.

15:29.972 --> 15:31.723
No, stop. He's right, though.

15:31.807 --> 15:33.434
Good. Good to meet you.

15:33.642 --> 15:37.312
But in the future, Mr. Gilbert
will sign off on any new hires.

15:38.480 --> 15:40.607
Uh... Yeah. Okay.

15:42.317 --> 15:46.822
-Oh... We're bringing in a boat tonight.
-Great. What time?

15:47.030 --> 15:48.198
Don't worry about it.

15:49.074 --> 15:52.578
I'm also gonna be upgrading the security
around the perimeter of this place.

15:53.162 --> 15:54.496
I'll get you a passcode.

15:55.497 --> 15:56.582
Okay, thanks.

16:12.973 --> 16:14.475
So, you're a good kid?

16:15.642 --> 16:16.643
Yes, sir.

16:17.728 --> 16:19.146
You respect your father?

16:21.106 --> 16:22.024
Yes, sir.

16:23.233 --> 16:24.860
It's important, respect.

16:28.572 --> 16:30.949
Being a father's a tough job, you know?

16:32.117 --> 16:35.245
I mean, it's hard to get it right...

16:36.622 --> 16:38.790
but we try, don't we?

16:40.000 --> 16:40.876
Yes, sir.

16:44.004 --> 16:46.465
Why don't you go ahead...?
Go ahead and tell him.

16:53.847 --> 16:55.182
I just wanted to thank you.

16:57.935 --> 17:00.312
For sending money to my mom
all these years.

17:04.525 --> 17:06.276
We need it, so thanks.

17:14.910 --> 17:17.371
Hey, why don't you...?

17:17.454 --> 17:19.414
You go wait in the car for me

17:19.498 --> 17:22.417
because I gotta have
a couple words with Dad, okay?

17:29.383 --> 17:30.634
It was good meeting you, son.

17:34.513 --> 17:35.597
See you.

17:44.731 --> 17:48.277
So, we went to a beach. That doesn't...
That doesn't prove anything.

17:48.360 --> 17:50.779
It makes our whole story
complete bullshit.

17:56.368 --> 17:57.869
Eric O'Bannon.

17:59.830 --> 18:03.333
Eric O'Bannon can fuck everything for us.

18:10.549 --> 18:11.925
Can't John do something?

18:14.052 --> 18:15.137
-What?
-I don't know.

18:15.804 --> 18:19.057
Bring him in on some made-up
bullshit charge. Anything.

18:25.731 --> 18:26.898
Fuck.

18:36.825 --> 18:38.827
All right, so if John won't do anything...

18:40.287 --> 18:41.163
Yeah?

18:43.874 --> 18:45.375
What are we gonna do...

18:46.001 --> 18:46.918
you and me?

19:04.978 --> 19:06.480
O'Bannon.

19:09.441 --> 19:11.985
Jesus. My mom's sleeping, dude.

19:12.444 --> 19:13.528
Fuck.

19:16.114 --> 19:17.449
Tell me everything.

19:19.451 --> 19:21.244
Okay. About what?

19:22.913 --> 19:24.706
About that fucking family.

19:27.000 --> 19:30.087
I want everything. I want it all now.

19:31.129 --> 19:32.589
I fucking told you everything.

19:33.674 --> 19:35.926
-So, what were you gonna tell the cops?
-Nothing.

19:36.593 --> 19:37.803
Nothing. That's bullshit.

19:38.762 --> 19:40.305
Come on, bro. Don't hold out on me.

19:40.514 --> 19:43.850
I'm not fucking holding out on you.
I fucking told you everything. Okay?

19:48.647 --> 19:50.482
No. Oh, no.

19:50.899 --> 19:52.734
No, man. No. No.

19:52.818 --> 19:55.612
You stupid fuckbrain.
Did you turn him in already?

19:55.821 --> 19:57.364
You know what? Fuck you.

19:57.572 --> 19:59.324
I fucking told you everything. Fuck off.

19:59.741 --> 20:00.951
Oh.

20:01.868 --> 20:02.869
-No, no, no.
-Fuck what?

20:02.953 --> 20:04.871
-Put it fucking down.
-Shut the fuck up.

20:04.955 --> 20:07.165
- We can talk, all right?
- Shut up. Shut up.

20:08.750 --> 20:11.086
Don't you ever fucking push me again.

20:11.628 --> 20:14.923
-Ozzy, put the fucking gun down.
-Tell me everything you know right now.

20:15.132 --> 20:16.967
-I told you everything.
-Everything. Everything.

20:17.050 --> 20:18.885
Hey!

20:21.763 --> 20:22.889
Get out of here.

20:26.309 --> 20:27.477
Now.

20:28.311 --> 20:29.896
Fucking put it down.

20:31.690 --> 20:33.817
We were-- We were just finishing--
All right.

20:34.025 --> 20:36.570
We're just finishing up,
sweetheart. Just finishing up.

20:37.904 --> 20:39.865
Okay. See?

20:40.115 --> 20:41.908
We were just finishing up, sweetheart.

20:42.951 --> 20:44.035
- We're done.
- Ozzy.

20:44.619 --> 20:46.997
Ozzy. I fucking told you everything, okay?

20:47.372 --> 20:49.916
Yeah. Sure you did.

20:56.131 --> 20:58.258
Just go fucking sleep it off.

21:07.267 --> 21:08.101
Fuck.

21:10.270 --> 21:11.688
- Chelsea, what?
- I can't...

21:12.105 --> 21:13.940
These people you hang out with,
I swear to God.

21:14.024 --> 21:16.234
I don't hang out with him.
It's a business thing.

21:16.943 --> 21:18.153
It's on me, seriously?

21:18.361 --> 21:21.323
A guy comes over drunk as shit,
walks through the backyard

21:21.406 --> 21:23.408
with a fucking gun on me
and it's my fault?

21:32.250 --> 21:33.418
Are you okay?

21:33.502 --> 21:35.545
Yeah.

21:36.880 --> 21:38.006
Sorry, I'm... I...

21:39.174 --> 21:41.551
I don't usually drink
in the middle of the day.

21:41.635 --> 21:43.053
It's just, um...

21:46.056 --> 21:47.766
-I'm sorry.
-Eve.

21:48.391 --> 21:49.559
What?

21:52.020 --> 21:53.313
Is it that man?

22:00.946 --> 22:02.030
Who is he?

22:04.282 --> 22:05.367
My ex.

22:11.665 --> 22:12.958
He said he knew Danny.

22:18.672 --> 22:21.383
Eve. Please, just tell me.

22:25.136 --> 22:26.513
Him and Danny...

22:29.099 --> 22:30.559
robbed a drugstore.

22:34.312 --> 22:38.316
For pills... to sell on the street.

22:46.866 --> 22:47.784
But, you know...

22:49.578 --> 22:52.455
It wasn't... It wasn't like Danny
to do that kind of thing,

22:52.539 --> 22:55.000
but the restaurant was everything to him

22:55.083 --> 22:56.459
and he was gonna lose it, so...

22:57.335 --> 23:00.130
Whenever he needed money,
he always came to us. I...

23:01.006 --> 23:06.136
Danny was never shy...
about asking Robert for help.

23:08.388 --> 23:10.098
He did ask Robert for help.

23:19.316 --> 23:21.443
So, you come to me first.

23:23.278 --> 23:25.196
Have you talked to your siblings
about this?

23:26.865 --> 23:28.116
What, Meg and Kevin?

23:28.325 --> 23:30.660
They're not gonna be interested.
And John? I just...

23:33.788 --> 23:35.832
I don't wanna ask John for money anymore.

23:36.249 --> 23:38.710
But you got no problem coming to me...

23:40.211 --> 23:42.589
tapping the same vein over and over again.

23:50.055 --> 23:52.474
I'm taking responsibility
for my life, okay?

23:52.557 --> 23:56.603
I'm looking after the kid, I've done this,
I'm doing everything,

23:56.686 --> 23:58.813
everything that you've asked me to do.

23:59.648 --> 24:02.108
So, what do you want,
an award or something? I mean...

24:04.903 --> 24:06.988
It's called being an adult.

24:11.034 --> 24:14.120
Jesus, I just can't fucking win with you,
can I? I...

24:17.415 --> 24:18.917
I don't know, Dad, I just...

24:20.627 --> 24:22.754
I finally got my life together,

24:22.837 --> 24:24.964
and what, now you just
don't wanna hear about it?

24:25.465 --> 24:27.926
I've been hearing about it for decades.

24:31.721 --> 24:35.600
I know who I am now
and I know what I'm capable of,

24:35.684 --> 24:37.268
whether you believe it or not, Dad.

24:37.352 --> 24:38.353
I just...

24:40.105 --> 24:41.606
I just need a loan.

24:47.612 --> 24:50.115
So, you're ready to bet on yourself?

