and you were his brother.

54:23.428 --> 54:26.014
You should've fucking looked out
for him, but you didn't, did you?

54:26.097 --> 54:30.768
Fuck you!
You wanna put all this on me? Hm?

54:30.977 --> 54:34.355
Who introduced Danny
to Wayne Lowry, huh?

54:34.522 --> 54:38.776
Who the fuck had Danny
stealing gas, dealing drugs?

54:38.860 --> 54:40.820
I'll tell you who.

54:40.904 --> 54:44.574
It was that fucking dirtbag
Eric O'Bannon.

54:44.741 --> 54:47.243
That's who started this.

54:49.913 --> 54:52.874
You don't know anything
about my family.

54:53.917 --> 54:58.880
You have no idea what the fuck went on
inside of that fucking house of ours.

54:59.964 --> 55:01.716
You have no idea
how much I helped Danny,

55:01.799 --> 55:06.554
how much I fucking helped all of them.
No fucking idea.

55:07.931 --> 55:09.807
Is that your story?

55:11.643 --> 55:16.731
Because I gotta fucking tell my story,
John, and I think we'll see...

55:17.899 --> 55:19.484
who ends up on top.

55:39.254 --> 55:44.634
Yeah, now we get to the real point
of the conversation, don't we?

55:46.761 --> 55:49.514
The real John Rayburn, wow.

55:49.722 --> 55:53.184
I finally get to see the favorite son
rolling around

55:53.268 --> 55:55.436
in fucking shit
just like the rest of us.

55:55.520 --> 55:57.230
You need
to fucking stop talking right now.

55:57.313 --> 56:00.775
No, it's okay.
Put a fucking bullet in my head, John.

56:04.070 --> 56:05.947
Just fucking do it.

56:11.119 --> 56:14.163
There's no fucking way in the world
that I'll let my family lose everything

56:14.247 --> 56:16.583
because of you.
Do you understand that?

56:16.666 --> 56:18.418
Because of me?

56:22.088 --> 56:25.216
You're losing everything because you
killed your fucking brother, asshole!

56:30.263 --> 56:35.476
Go ahead. Anything to protect
the fucking Rayburn name. Right?

56:38.813 --> 56:40.607
Go ahead, John.

56:53.453 --> 56:54.537
Fuck.

57:05.632 --> 57:08.551
-I'll say hello to Danny.
-Fuck you!

57:13.056 --> 57:17.477
Anything to protect the Rayburn name.

58:32.301 --> 58:34.345
You tell your fucking story.

59:18.556 --> 59:19.974
What the fuck do you want, Kevin?

59:20.641 --> 59:23.478
I have to talk to you.
Can I come in for a minute?

59:26.105 --> 59:27.440
Okay.

59:32.403 --> 59:34.405
What do you wanna talk about?

59:42.955 --> 59:47.335
Listen, man, I know what's going on
between you and John.

59:47.502 --> 59:49.420
-I know everything.
-Oh, I know you do.

59:50.254 --> 59:54.342
-I know, but it's not what you think.
-No? What do I think?

59:54.675 --> 59:57.136
Look, Marco,
you have to understand, now,

59:57.220 --> 1:00:02.475
things got really, really fucked up
when Danny came home.

1:00:02.558 --> 1:00:06.187
It was... It was a crazy time,
and I had no choice--

1:00:06.354 --> 1:00:07.980
What'd you do?

1:00:11.025 --> 1:00:13.402
I had nothing to do with killing Danny.

1:00:14.362 --> 1:00:15.947
Well, you lied about it, right?

1:00:16.030 --> 1:00:18.825
So, you did have something
to do with killing Danny.

1:00:20.785 --> 1:00:24.789
Okay, but I wanna tell you
everything right now, okay?

1:00:24.872 --> 1:00:26.374
I wanna tell you the truth now.

1:00:26.457 --> 1:00:32.088
What is it about your fucking family
that you guys think that you can lie

1:00:32.171 --> 1:00:35.591
and lie and lie until it's convenient
to tell the truth?

1:00:35.758 --> 1:00:38.469
-I know. I know, we're fucked up.
-Yeah, you are fucked up.

1:00:38.553 --> 1:00:39.887
And we're not making a deal.

1:00:40.054 --> 1:00:42.181
Marco, just listen to me
for a second, man. Come on.

1:00:42.265 --> 1:00:45.351
You listen to me.
I have everything that I need.

1:00:45.518 --> 1:00:48.354
I wanna tell you right now, all right?
I wanna tell you everything now.

1:00:48.521 --> 1:00:50.231
Get the fuck out of--

1:00:51.983 --> 1:00:53.943
-What is it, O'Bannon?
-Fuck.

1:00:54.026 --> 1:00:57.738
- <i>We need to fucking talk now.</i>
- Well, we're set up for tomorrow.

1:00:57.822 --> 1:01:00.783
<i>No. John Rayburn</i>
<i>is going fucking nuts.</i>

1:01:00.950 --> 1:01:03.828
I either talk right now,
or I don't fucking talk at all.

1:01:03.995 --> 1:01:07.832
All right, calm down.
Calm down, Eric, okay?

1:01:08.040 --> 1:01:10.543
Meet me at the station in 20 minutes,
we'll figure this out.

1:01:10.710 --> 1:01:12.503
<i>I don't have a fucking car here, man.</i>

1:01:12.712 --> 1:01:14.505
Where are you? I'll pick you up.

1:01:14.672 --> 1:01:17.258
I'm at the shack by Fairview Harbor.

1:01:17.466 --> 1:01:20.595
All right, I'm on my way.

1:01:21.721 --> 1:01:25.391
Look, man, I'm begging you now.
I have a baby coming.

1:01:26.392 --> 1:01:28.686
-Kevin.
-Please, just listen to me.

1:01:29.937 --> 1:01:32.148
Get the fuck out of my house.

1:01:46.495 --> 1:01:48.331
It was John.

1:02:36.671 --> 1:02:38.172
Meg.

1:02:43.344 --> 1:02:45.179
John did it.

1:02:47.640 --> 1:02:49.100
No shit.

1:02:52.436 --> 1:02:54.605
And you guys helped him.

1:02:54.689 --> 1:02:58.526
And the three of you are going
to fucking prison.

1:02:58.734 --> 1:03:02.863
So, do me a favor, all right,
and get the fuck out of my hou--

1:03:19.255 --> 1:03:21.257
Feels good, doesn't it?

1:03:26.137 --> 1:03:28.681
You should let them take care of it.

1:03:37.023 --> 1:03:38.899
Where are we going?

1:04:18.064 --> 1:04:19.357
Mom...

1:04:21.609 --> 1:04:23.069
Honey.

1:04:23.611 --> 1:04:26.489
What is it? What is it?

1:04:30.409 --> 1:04:32.995
Mom, there's something
you need to know.

1:04:39.960 --> 1:04:41.295
Yeah.

1:04:42.088 --> 1:04:43.422
Fuck it.

1:04:45.716 --> 1:04:47.385
Just drive.

