<i>♪ It might be nice to disappear ♪</i>

1:05:42.440 --> 1:05:46.652
<i>♪ To have a vanishing act ♪</i>

1:05:46.986 --> 1:05:51.115
<i>♪ To always be looking forward ♪</i>

1:05:52.116 --> 1:05:56.120
<i>♪ Never look over your back ♪</i>

