<i>♪ It must be nice to disappear ♪</i>

1:06:03.961 --> 1:06:08.048
<i>♪ Float into a mist ♪</i>

1:06:11.135 --> 1:06:15.973
<i>♪ It must be nice to disappear ♪</i>

